# From https://github.com/eyereasoner/eye/blob/master/reasoning/basic-monadic/
# (query.n3's 10-way cycle-detection rule over graphgen.n3-generated data).
#
# BLOCKED: the rule `{?R :cycle (?D0 ?D1 ... ?D9 ?D0)} <= {?D0 ?R ?D1. ...
