# doesn't implement (see good_cobbler.n3's blocking-reason comment) -- here
# to detect a repeated variable (?D0) closing the cycle inside a 11-element
# list pattern -- plus its accompanying 1tt*.ttl fixture files are randomly
# generated benchmark data (10^n triples) rather than a small illustrative
# fact set. Out of scope; not vendored as runnable input.
